VB'a HShMSh VTHUr V'aChUr Y'aKL MN-HQDShYM KY LChMV HV'a.
NBLH VTUrPhH L'a Y'aKL LTM'aH-BH 'aNY YHVH.
VShMUrV 'aTh-MShMUrThY VL'a-YSh'aV 'yLYV ChT'a VMThV BV KY YChLLHV 'aNY YHVH MQDShM.
VKL-ZUr L'a-Y'aKL QDSh ThVShB KHN VShKYUr L'a-Y'aKL QDSh.
VKHN KY-YQNH NPhSh QNYN KSPhV HV'a Y'aKL BV VYLYD BYThV HM Y'aKLV BLChMV.
VBTh-KHN KY ThHYH L'aYSh ZUr HV'a BThUrVMTh HQDShYM L'a Th'aKL.
